channel.title: Expand Your Musical Horizons
channel.description: podcasts of independent, intelligent, electronic music from around the world
channel.copyright: copyrights to the individual artists represented on the podcast; see link for further details

item.title: Magnatune Downtempo podcast
item.description: A sampling of downtempo and chillout grooves from magnatune.com artists, including Ashwan, Dr. Kuch, Artemis, Ammonite, Trancevision, Lizzi, Mr. Epic, Etherfysh, Curl, Stargarden, and Mr. Gelatine . Find them at www.magnatune.com.

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 03
item.description: 10 downtempo tracks, including the Warheads, Steffan Coonan, Maido Project, Christophe Goze, Briareus, Gum, After Touch, UGene, Comp133t, and DJ Eric III, provided by the Podshow Podsafe Music Network (music.podshow.com).

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 04
item.description: 7 downtempo and spoken-word tracks, many of them provided by the Podshow Podsafe Music Network. Also includes independent artists "Upsurge!"

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 05
item.description: A collection of 11 podsafe-friendly downtempo and trip-hop tracks from various independent artists, provided by the Podshow Podsafe Music Network (music.podshow.com).

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 06, m4a
item.description: Enhanced version of this podcast (shows album covers, plays in AAC format)...same 12 downtempo and dub tracks as the .mp3 version: from independent artists who make their music available through the Podshow Podsafe Music Network (music.podshow.com), Magnatune (www.magnatune.com) and ccMIxter (www.ccmixter.org).

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 06, mp3
item.description: This episode features Briareus, Williamson, Yongen, Plunkett, Christophe Goze, Justin Bianco, Mister Fusty, Burning Babylon, Hoxman, _ghost, Budha Building, and Slot Car Racers

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 07
item.description: Downtempo tracks from Evolve, Aphilas, Sofia Rueda, Oveloe, JCRZ, Vate, Briareus, genox, and Disciples of Ageema.

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 08
item.description: 9 chilling tracks from Electrix (Germany), Zico (Poland), Karmacoda (San Francisco), the Warheads (San Francisco), Mixro (ccMixter), micropixie (San Francisco), JCRZ (France), Vate (Mexico), and genox (Switzerland). Links to all artists and purchase information (when applicable) at http://www.carynorsworthy.com/podcasts.html.

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 09, the Eastern Europe and Russia episode
item.description: 9 downtempo and ambient tracks from artists in the Russian Federation, Poland, Slovakia, and Lithuania, who release their music on the internet through netlabels and through Magnatune.com and Jamendo.com. Track/artist/label information is available at http://www.carynorsworthy.com/podcasts.html

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 10
item.description: Chilled-out tracks that venture from eastern grooves to lush orchestral soundscapes to trip hop, IDM, and ambient beats. Artists include Koan, Kadang, Phundamental, the Winston Giles Orchestra, redzone, Calm Be, Confused Man, Sumergido, Aligning Minds,and Effect Unit. Come along for the ride. Track/artist/label information is available at http://www.carynorsworthy.com/podcasts.html

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 11 - the Germany Episode
item.description: Tracks that are specifically from German artists, ranging from downtempo to eastern grooves to lush orchestral soundscapes to trip hop, IDM, and ambient beats. Artists include Undo Silence, Alec Troniq, DJ Ax, Spheric Lounge, Dorntec, Calm Be, Confused Man, Ambrish, Cantaloup, Electrix, and Echofloat. Special guest: Andreas of XtraChill. Come along for the ride. Track/artist/label information is available at http://www.carynorsworthy.com/podcasts.html

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 12
item.description: Downtempo to eastern grooves to lush orchestral soundscapes to trip hop, nu-jazz, and ambient beats. Artists include: Superbus, Pendle, Madstyle, DS-ARt, Mister Fusty, Pipe Choir, Peacespeakers, Confused Man, Spinmeister, cdk, dsy, and Sawtooth. Track/artist/label information is available at http://www.carynorsworthy.com/podcasts.html

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 13
item.description: Downtempo to ambient and world fusion grooves. Artists include: Superbus, JCRZ, Madstyle, Soundshifter, Liquid Zen, Sonmi 451, Peacespeakers, and Fromuz. Track/artist/label information is available at http://www.carynorsworthy.com/podcasts.html

item.title: Special Interview - Maido Project
item.description: An interview recoorded live in the 11eme arrondissement of Paris with Pierre Baillot of The Maido Project, a nujazz/world fusion ensemble. Includes some Maido Project tracks from their two albums, which are also available for sale in iTunes. Track information is available at http://www.carynorsworthy.com/podcasts.html

item.title: Downtempo Podcast 14
